MVP Scope (aim for this)
 Create a contract and get a shareable link
 Real-time term editing visible to both parties
 Negotiation log showing who proposed what
 Hold-to-seal mechanic (both must hold simultaneously)
 Sealed contracts are read-only and permanent
 Clerk auth gates editing to the two signatories
Stretch Goals (if you're flying)
 Contract expiry — unsealed contracts self-destruct after 24h
 Witness mode — a third party can observe but not edit
 Contract gallery — a public feed of (opted-in) sealed deals
 Share card — an OG image generated for the sealed URL